{"tid":2045552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國亞特蘭大兩名警員示威中使用過度武力被革職 市長稱永遠不能接受用「巨大壓力」為自己開脫","createTime":"2020-06-01T01:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T04:46:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f78ff1410dcbc21d9c9dd5a2030f5db9d022a948","tid":2045552,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T01:33:53.000Z","msg":"亞特蘭大兩名警員使用過度武力被革職<br />\n01.06.2020 09:06<br />\n<br />\n在佐治亞州亞特蘭大，兩名警員處理示威時使用過度武力而被革職。早前有片段顯示，兩名涉事警員對兩名黑人大學生使用電擊槍，然後把他們拖出車外。<br />\n<br />\n市長宣佈兩名警員被革職的消息，批評事件令人不安，又說理解警員在巨大壓力下長時間工作，但使用過分武力是永遠不能接受。另外，三名與事件有關的警員已被調往文職崗位，當局會審視他們的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1296073&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1296073%26csid%3D261_367&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=ef9209b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1296073&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"33f4d81e44f83ca40166231641bab68fc7bd3d45","tid":2045552,"uid":36104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T01:36:31.000Z","msg":"有冇香港特務比較圖"},{"pid":"dad42c3e93d7a4d7ec94fe0cf430fcd568944778","tid":2045552,"uid":357030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T01:39:36.000Z","msg":"藍屍: 我睇唔到"},{"pid":"5762e215598b5bfec7838c452b3ca153371d9d5e","tid":2045552,"uid":8308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好推 一陣被D藍屍見到唔知會唔會發癲"},{"pid":"dff8f188111dd62ccb96f5d04c4b6d79fb7fe9d3","tid":2045552,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"香港<br />\n<br />\n你地無做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我道你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n道歉? 你地快啲同我道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi